```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant AdminDashboard
    participant LoadingOrchestrator
    participant UserCounter
    participant DataPanel
    participant PartnersCard
    participant API
    
    User->>AdminDashboard: Acessa dashboard
    
    activate AdminDashboard
    AdminDashboard->>LoadingOrchestrator: useLoadingOrchestrator()
    activate LoadingOrchestrator
    LoadingOrchestrator-->>AdminDashboard: { isLoading, register, setLoading }
    deactivate LoadingOrchestrator
    
    AdminDashboard->>User: Mostra Loading Spinner<br/>(isLoading = true)
    
    par Componentes se registram
        AdminDashboard->>UserCounter: renderiza
        activate UserCounter
        UserCounter->>LoadingOrchestrator: register('userCounter')
        LoadingOrchestrator-->>UserCounter: componentId
        UserCounter->>API: GET /api/users-count
        API-->>UserCounter: { count: 42 }
        UserCounter->>LoadingOrchestrator: setLoading('userCounter', false)
        deactivate UserCounter
    and
        AdminDashboard->>DataPanel: renderiza
        activate DataPanel
        DataPanel->>LoadingOrchestrator: register('dataPanel')
        LoadingOrchestrator-->>DataPanel: componentId
        DataPanel->>API: GET /api/admin/clients-with-collection-summary
        API-->>DataPanel: { clients: [...] }
        DataPanel->>LoadingOrchestrator: setLoading('dataPanel', false)
        deactivate DataPanel
    and
        AdminDashboard->>PartnersCard: renderiza
        activate PartnersCard
        PartnersCard->>LoadingOrchestrator: register('partnersCard')
        LoadingOrchestrator-->>PartnersCard: componentId
        PartnersCard->>API: GET /api/admin/partners/overview
        API-->>PartnersCard: { partners: [...] }
        PartnersCard->>LoadingOrchestrator: setLoading('partnersCard', false)
        deactivate PartnersCard
    end
    
    Note over LoadingOrchestrator: Verifica automaticamente:<br/>Object.values(loadingStates).every(s => !s)
    
    LoadingOrchestrator->>AdminDashboard: isLoading = false
    AdminDashboard->>User: Esconde Loading Spinner
    AdminDashboard->>User: Mostra Dashboard Completo
    deactivate AdminDashboard
    
    Note right of LoadingOrchestrator: ✅ Benefícios:<br/>- 1 hook centralizado<br/>- Auto-registro de componentes<br/>- Lógica encapsulada<br/>- Complexidade: O(1)<br/>- Fácil adicionar componentes
```
